  <div id=PPTP10 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0010.htm');" id=PPTL10>Four adjacent Squares</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC10 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Consider four adjacent squares</li>
   <ul>
    <li>2, 4, and 8 squares</li>
    <li>m<sub>0</sub>+m<sub>2</sub>+m<sub>4</sub>+m<sub>6</sub> =
        x'y'z'+x'yz'+xy'z'+xyz' = x'z'(y'+y) +xz'(y'+y) = x'z' + xzë = z'</li>
    <li>m<sub>1</sub>+m<sub>3</sub>+m<sub>5</sub>+m<sub>7</sub> =
        x'y'z+x'yz+xy'z+xyz =x'z(y'+y) + xz(y'+y) =x'z + xz = z</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
