  <ul>
   <li>Example 3.4: let F = A'C + A'B + AB'C + BC</li>
   <ul>
    <li>Express it in sum of minterms.</li>
    <li>Find the minimal sum of products expression.</li>
    <li>Ans:</li>
    <li>	F(A, B, C) = S(1, 2, 3, 5, 7) = C + A'B</li>
    <br>
    <br>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
