   <li>Consider F(A, B, C, D) = &#931;(0, 2, 3, 5, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 13, 15)</li>
   <ul>
    <li>The simplified expression may not be unique</li>
    <li>F	= BD+B'D'+CD+AD = BD+B'D'+CD+AB'</li>
    <li><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>†††††† </span>	= BD+B'D'+B'C+AD =
        BD+B'D'+B'C+AB'</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
   <br>
