   <ul>
    <li>Can be implemented as 0 or 1</li>
   </ul>
   <li>Example 3.9: simplify F(w, x, y, z) = S(1, 3, 7, 11, 15) which has the
       don't-care conditions d(w, x, y, z) = S(0, 2, 5).</li>
