  <ul>
   <li>Wired logic</li>
   <ul>
    <li>A wire connection between the outputs of two gates</li>
    <li>Open-collector TTL NAND gates: wired-AND logic</li>
    <li>The NOR output of ECL gates: wired-OR logic</li>
