 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>40</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP40 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0040.htm');" id=PPTL40>Non-degenerate Forms</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC40 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>16 possible combinations of two-level forms</li>
   <ul>
    <li>Eight of them: degenerate forms = a single operation</li>
    <ul>
     <li>AND-AND, AND-NAND, OR-OR, OR-NOR, NAND-OR, NAND-NOR, NOR-AND,
         NOR-NAND.</li>
    </ul>
    <li>The eight non-degenerate forms</li>
    <ul>
     <li>AND-OR, OR-AND, NAND-NAND, NOR-NOR, NOR-OR, NAND-AND, OR-NAND,
         AND-NOR.</li>
     <li>AND-OR and NAND-NAND = sum of products.</li>
     <li>OR-AND and NOR-NOR = product of sums.</li>
     <li>NOR-OR, NAND-AND, OR-NAND, AND-NOR = ?</li>
    </ul>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>41</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP41 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0041.htm');" id=PPTL41>AND-OR-Invert
  Implementation</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC41 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>AND-OR-INVERT (AOI) Implementation</li>
   <ul>
    <li>NAND-AND = AND-NOR = AOI</li>
    <li>F = (AB+CD+E)'</li>
    <li>F' = AB+CD+E<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>†† </span>(sum of products)</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>42</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP42 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0042.htm');" id=PPTL42>OR-AND-Invert
  Implementation</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC42 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>OR-AND-INVERT (OAI) Implementation</li>
   <ul>
    <li>OR-NAND = NOR-OR = OAI</li>
    <li>F = ((A+B)(C+D)E)'</li>
    <li>F' = (A+B)(C+D)E<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>†† </span>(product of
        sums)</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>43</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP43 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0043.htm');" id=PPTL43>Tabular Summary and
  Examples</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC43 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Example 3-11: F = x'y'z'+xyz'</li>
   <ul>
    <li>F' = x'y+xy'+z 		(F': sum of products)</li>
    <li>F = (x'y+xy'+z)' 		(F: AOI implementation)</li>
    <li>F = x'y'z' + xyz'		(F: sum of products)</li>
    <li>F' = (x+y+z)(x'+y'+z) 	(F': product of sums)</li>
    <li>F = ((x+y+z)(x'+y'+z))'	(F: OAI)</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>44</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP44 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0044.htm');" id=PPTL44>Tabular Summary and
  Examples</a></font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>45</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP45 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0045.htm');" id=PPTL45><span
  style='mso-spacerun:yes'>†</span></a></font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>46</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP46 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0046.htm');" id=PPTL46>3-9	Exclusive-OR
  Function</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC46 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Exclusive-OR (XOR)</li>
   <ul>
    <li>x≈y = xy'+x'y</li>
   </ul>
   <li>Exclusive-NOR (XNOR)</li>
   <ul>
    <li>(x≈y)' = xy + x'y'</li>
   </ul>
   <li>Some identities</li>
   <ul>
    <li>x≈0 = x</li>
    <li>x≈1 = x'</li>
    <li>x≈x = 0</li>
    <li>x≈x' = 1</li>
    <li>x≈y' = (x≈y)'</li>
    <li>x'≈y = (x≈y)'</li>
   </ul>
   <li>Commutative and associative</li>
   <ul>
    <li>A≈B = B≈A</li>
    <li>(A≈B) ≈C = A≈ (B≈C) = A≈B≈C</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>47</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP47 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0047.htm');" id=PPTL47>Exclusive-OR
  Implementations</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC47 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Implementations</li>
   <ul>
    <li>(x'+y')x + (x'+y')y = xy'+x'y = x≈y</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>48</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP48 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0048.htm');" id=PPTL48>Odd Function</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC48 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <ul>
    <li>A≈B≈C = (AB'+A'B)C' +(AB+A'B')C = AB'C'+A'BC'+ABC+A'B'C = S(1, 2, 4, 7)</li>
    <li>XOR is a odd function &#8594; an odd number of 1's, then F = 1.</li>
    <li>XNOR is a even function &#8594; an even number of 1's, then F = 1.</li>
    <br>
    <br>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>49</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP49 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0049.htm');" id=PPTL49>XOR and XNOR</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC49 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Logic diagram of odd and even functions</li>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>50</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP50 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0050.htm');" id=PPTL50>Four-variable
  Exclusive-OR function</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC50 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Four-variable Exclusive-OR function</li>
   <ul>
    <li>A≈B≈C≈D = (AB'+A'B)≈(CD'+C'D) = (AB'+A'B)(CD+C'D')+(AB+A'B')(CD'+C'D)</li>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr onmouseover="Over(this)" onmouseout="Out(this)" onclick="Follow(this)"
  style='cursor:hand'>
  <td align=right valign=top>
  <div class=sldNum><font size=2>51</font></div>
  </td>
  <td>
  <div id=PPTP51 class=PTxt><font size=2><a
  href="javascript:GoToSld('slide0051.htm');" id=PPTL51>Parity Generation and
  Checking</a></font></div>
  <div id=PPTC51 class=CTxt style='display:none'><font size=2>
  <ul>
   <li>Parity Generation and Checking</li>
   <ul>
    <li>A parity bit: P = x≈y≈z</li>
    <li>Parity check: C = x≈y≈z≈P</li>
    <ul>
     <li>C=1: one bit error or an odd number of data bit error</li>
     <li>C=0: correct or an even # of data bit error</li>
    </ul>
   </ul>
   <br>
  </ul>
  </font></div>
  </td>
 </tr>
